snippet.title: Air Strike USA gameplay (PC Game, 1990)
snippet.description:
Introduction and gameplay for Air Strike USA, Dos PC game produced by Digital Integration in 1990 - http://www.squakenet.com/download/air-strike-usa/3816/
Airstrike USA is an arcade action flight game, where you fly on various missions around the world. Missions include destroying enemy submarines, radars, aircraft, bases.
Played through Dosbox emulation platform.
Recorded with original sound.
